element.name: Firefly series - #7 - Kaylee by AbbeyAckbar, Traditional Cache (2.5/1.5)

long-description.center:
This cache is one of 11 caches in the firefly series.
Press : HERE to learn more.
Clip of Kaylee from the Firefly pilot episode 'Serenity'.Press : PLAY
long-description.p: The cache is located at the Hole in the wall beach (Burrow beach). We have included a waypoint for the entrance to the beach which is closer to the cache than the entrance for the 'Hole In the Wall' cache for those wanting a shorter walk.

Parking is available on Burrow road. Alternatively, you could take the Dart to Sutton train station or get the 31, 31B or 31C bus which serve Sutton and walk to the cache from there. Please enjoy a walk along the beach, but:

p.b: BE WARY OF TIDAL CHANNELS AROUND LOW WATER.

long-description.p: The beach backs up to a golf course. There is no need to access the golf course to get to the cache. Watch out for stray golfballs! : )

As for the cache itself, well it's completely in keeping with the character of Kaylee : )
and blends in well with it's surroundings.

p.b:
Feel free to post photos from your trip to the cache but
PLEASE don't post photos of the cache container to your log.

marquee.strong: Congratulations to hollmanr on the FTF!

groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:long_description:
This cache is one of 11 caches in the firefly series.
Press : HERE to learn more.


Clip of Kaylee from the Firefly pilot episode 'Serenity'.Press : PLAY

The cache

The cache is located at the Hole in the wall beach (Burrow beach). We have included a waypoint for the entrance to the beach which is closer to the cache than the entrance for the 'Hole In the Wall' cache for those wanting a shorter walk.

Parking is available on Burrow road. Alternatively, you could take the Dart to Sutton train station or get the 31, 31B or 31C bus which serve Sutton and walk to the cache from there. Please enjoy a walk along the beach, but:

BE WARY OF TIDAL CHANNELS AROUND LOW WATER.

The beach backs up to a golf course. There is no need to access the golf course to get to the cache. Watch out for stray golfballs! : )

As for the cache itself, well it's completely in keeping with the character of Kaylee : )
and blends in well with it's surroundings.

Feel free to post photos from your trip to the cache but
PLEASE don't post photos of the cache container to your log.



Congratulations to hollmanr on the FTF!
